-dimensional\nregime. This proof-of-principle illustration is expected to represent a\npractically feasible way to generate and observe this rogue wave in realistic\ncurrent ultracold atom experimental settings.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Dec 2021 17:30:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 12 Dec 2021 17:13:20 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 27 May 2022 13:31:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-30"}
