ined information flow and the difference of the four-body\ncorrelation and the two-body correlation explain the difference of the free\nenergy transport in secondary active and passive transport.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Dec 2021 22:32:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 20 Apr 2022 02:07:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-23"}
