panied by an indirect-direct band-gap transition for the CuInP$_2$Se$_6$\nmonolayer. Our study offers an effective approach to tune the FE and electronic\nproperties of ABP$_2$X$_6$ thin films for applications in electronics and\noptoelectronics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 Dec 2021 01:55:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-09"}
