. The peaks are likely\nrelated to the galaxy projected separation or the stage of the interaction\nprocess of a galaxy pair.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 Dec 2021 04:50:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 28 Feb 2022 08:09:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-04"}
