S-based method by a fair margin. Test on real TerraSAR-X data\nwith just 6 interferograms also shows high-quality 3-D reconstruction with\nhigh-density detected double scatterers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 Dec 2021 10:17:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-04"}
