ation instance. Extensive\nablations on two VidSGG datasets have attested to the effectiveness of our\nframework and BIG. Code is available at https://github.com/Dawn-LX/VidSGG-BIG.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 Dec 2021 10:49:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 3 Mar 2022 09:05:21 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 14 Mar 2022 14:53:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-15"}
