 tree diagram bound which has sufficed for higher\ndimensions needed to be supplemented by a singular correction. Its presence was\nestablished through multi-scale analysis in a recent joint work with HDC.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 Dec 2021 11:49:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 30 Sep 2022 15:45:15 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 3 Oct 2022 10:51:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-04"}
